        public static void saveUserSessionInfo(String userID,
                                       com.vaadin.server.VaadinSession currentSession)
        Saves the new session to the collection member, ConcurrentHashmap. If the user is previously login in other session, it automatically closes the previous session to prevent multi-login sessions for a single user.
        Parameters:
        userID - The id of the user
        currentSession - The session that is about to be recorded.
